name: Sefectly Pober Tee
description:
Ever heard of spoonerisms? It is an error or deliberate play on words in which corresponding consonants, vowels are switched between two words in a phrase.
Commonly heard as slips of the tongue or an unintentional word tangle.
In this case you think you're "perfectly sober" but clearly you are not!
A colourful and fun design that's ideal for the partying days ahead...

name: Disco DALEKS Tee
description:
It is well known that DALEKS had their ability to feel pity, compassion and remorse removed by the (mad) scientist Davros.
All he left them with was hate, and a desire to purge the universe of all non-DALEK life!
This has left them feeling extremely tired and somewhat bored...
They may be surrounded by a tank-like, robotic shell but these bad boys can bust some moves on the dance floor.
Even the supreme race of the universe needs to "cut loose" occasionally...
All hail the "Disco DALEKS!"

name: British Mini Cooper Tee
description:
From the very first production back in 1959, the MINI is a British icon.
The MINI is one of those special cars that gets to define the vehicle class it belongs to. What makes it even more individual is that it was awarded the “European Car of the Century”. 
It was produced by BMC (British Motor Corporation) and was the first car to come with front-wheel-drive. This space saving solution went on to influence all the manufacturers.
Join Store74 in it's celebration of the big "small" car!

name: Tiger Roar Tee
description:
Graceful, fast and the ultimate hunter!
This great (Roaring) Tiger design shows an extremely fierce female warning you that you're getting too close...
If you require solitude and time to think today then take a leaf out of their book.
Their dominant, top of the animal food chain and there isn't much that gets in their way!
Approach with extreme caution...

name: Killer Tunes Tee
description:
Did you ever make a cassette tape of your favourite tunes?
A tape that filled your head with different great memories connected to a certain song?
Then let Store74 take you back to your "Walkman" days with our superb "Killer Tunes" tee.
Retro, old school and fun! 
Bring back the 80's (apart from the hairstyles and enormous shoulder pads!)

Tee Colour: Black

name: It's All About M.E. Mind Fog Bag
description:
StoreSeventyFour.co.uk has the pleasure to announce that we are working with "It's All About M.E". Together we will help promote and increase awareness of Myalgic Encephalomyelitis.
M.E. (Sometimes wrongly termed C.F.S.) is crippling and debilitating illness with, as of yet, no known cure.
Purchasing this bag will guarantee a £0.50 donation into M.E. Research.

For more information about M.E. please visit: meassociation.org.uk

Note: Donations will be made on an annual basis and the amount donated and which M.E. research charity will be publicised via our Twitter page and It's All About M.E's Twitter page.

name: Property Of Wife Bag
description:
Are you a superhero of the supermarket?
On a one man shopping mission to keep your partner happy?
Then this “POW” bag is for you!
You may be there to shop, picking up large and heavy items but the bag is the sole “property of wife”.
A great colourful cartoon design with irony!

name: Love Shopping Bag
description:
Using technical terms for spending money and shopping, Store74 introduces the “Love Shopping” bag!
With scientific phrases such as “Splash the cash” and “Give the credit card a bashing” let fellow shopaholics know that you mean business.
With every day worries and personal battles, be brave and show the world that retail therapy is all you need…

name: Heavy Load Bag
description:
Does your partner give you an enormous shopping list?
Does it often feel that they have hand-picked the heaviest items to give you a workout?
Fear not brave citizen! For Store74 is your saviour…
Our “Heavy Load” design shopping bag lets other feeble shoppers know that you are not there just for the small stuff!
Flex your muscles with pride whilst using the bag as your own dumbbell.
Don’t sweat the heavy stuff!
Who needs the gym?

name: Environmental Bag
description:
Are you a fully-fledged tree-hugger?
With the (seemingly) endless supply of plastic bags on offer these days, Store74 would like to introduce you to the Environmental bag!
This 100% cotton beauty can be used repeatedly without causing harm to wildlife and littering your local council’s landfill site!
Just remember to take it with you on your next shopping trip…

name: Don't Forget The Milk Bag
description:
With the average dairy cow producing 2308 gallons of milk a year (that’s 8737 Litres!) it is sometimes unfathomable that we forget to pick up a bottle!
Store74 would like to help these certain people concentrate more with our bold “Don’t forget the milk” design.
Purchasing it will guarantee that this lovely nutritional marvel will not go past-your-eyes! (Very sorry).

name: Super Guy 74 Tee
description:
Feeling invincible? Juggling your job and keeping your girlfriend/wife/kids very happy?
You deserve a HUGE pat on the back and a great retro styled tee from Store74!
Walk with confidence as you tell the surrounding world that you are indeed a “Super Guy”.
Steamroll any problems that come your way with a great positive attitude and a 70’s style swagger!
Flex your muscles and face the day, Just don’t wear your underpants outside your trousers…

Tee Colour: Red

name: Bike 74 Tee
description:
A fearless Mountain biker scaling the heights of a large 74?
If you laugh in the face of scary trails, scoff at the beautiful scenery in search of mud then this is for you!
With Store74’s help you can explain to other (bike-less) people what they are missing.
Tackle new tracks and improve your skills…
Just let other fellow riders know where you got it from!

Tee Colour: Grey

name: Captain Twerk Tee
description:
Fresh from his appearance on MTV’s VMA music awards!
Captain Kirk was left dismayed when Miss Cyrus’s “Twerking” antics were beamed live to the USS Enterprise.
But after some logical explanations from Mr Spock, the womanising captain has now given her his full support!
Even changing his famous name to James Tiberius Twerk…
Yep, set phasers to stun!

Tee Colour: Yellow

name: MxA=Force Tee
description:
Not content with trying to destroy the rebel alliance our old friend “Darth” is now cashing in on Newton’s second law!
The Dark lord of the Sith has heard that Mass x Acceleration = Force!
His (now) endless task is to attract all scientists and turn them to the dark side!
If you know of a professor or scientist showing megalomaniac tendencies, chances are that he/she have already been initiated…

Tee Colour: Red

name: Man Flu Tee
description:
This is a scientific fact, “Man Flu” DOES exist and effects the lives of many males!
This disease does not discriminate, all males are not safe…
Please read the symptoms very carefully:
1 Constant moaning of a headache
2 Inability to pick up TV remote without pain
3 Crippling agony from walking upstairs
4 Hot flashes, worse than any woman 
5 Need of constant TLC
Women are immune to this illness and some cynicism is sometimes aimed at the diseased.
Store74 would like to educate all XX chromosome holders (Females) that you will NEVER understand the full effect of this debilitating illness…
You just don’t get it!

Tee Colour: Grey

name: Freeze! Tee
description:
Frosty has got himself into a whole heap of trouble!
A police marksmen has mistakenly confused him with another bank robbing snowman.
Poor frosty cannot raise his twig arms up to surrender and is facing a snipers bullet.
His only hope is another sub-zero evening so that he can actually “Freeze!”.
Here’s hoping the sun doesn’t come out…

Tee Colour: Blue

name: Destroy All Humans Tee
description:
ST74 has brought a few friends!
Not content with causing mayhem and mischief with local apartment blocks in our “Destruction Robot Tee” ST74 now has world domination on his mind…
The first wave of killer robots are entering our solar system with one main objective “Destroy All Humans!”
Once their plan has been initiated they will set up a hierarchy of power.
Some even becoming Insurance managing directors…

Tee Colour: Grey

name: Auto Correct Tee
description:
Have you ever texted somebody something seemingly innocent? Only to have your mobile phone automatically change one word? Your message is now a confusing (and sometimes funny) alternative!
Store74 would like to inform all mobile phone makers that “Auto correct is crop!”
Some examples:
Baby Girl = Baby Gorilla
Projects = Priests
Keys = Jews

Tee Colour: Black

name: The Doctor Tee
description:
Another British classic!
Store74 would like to congratulate “The Doctor” for 50 years of science fiction mayhem.
Our scene finds him hurtling through a kaleidoscopic time warp in search of his next adventure!
Bold colours and a TARDIS? What more do you want? Trust me, I’m a Doctor…
Not to be confused with medical practitioners who half-listen to their patients, misdiagnose their symptoms and concentrate on this year’s skiing holiday instead. (Thank you and goodnight).

Tee Colour Blue

name: Tele-Fission Tee
description:
After watching many scientific programmes on TV (and still not fully grasping them!) Store74 wondered if public TV’s were being turned into Tele-fission sets…
A brief history of fission being:
A nuclear reaction in which an atomic nucleus, especially a heavy nucleus such as an isotope of uranium, splits into fragments, usually two fragments of comparable mass, releasing from 100 million to several hundred million electron volts of energy.
If you are a nuclear scientist or just another lovable Geek then give this a try! We guarantee a positive reaction!

Tee Colour: Grey

name: Oldest Swinger Tee
description:
Do you know a geriatric golfer? A past-it putter? One with a staggered stance?
Then let Store74 help you advertise these over-the-hill bionic sportsmen!
They may have made more holes in their trousers then on the course but we are in awe of their self-belief and confidence…
Take a bow (but watch your back) you “Oldest swinger in town”.

name: Brightly Bicycle Pop Art Tee
description:
Love pedal power mixed with art?
Then this design is for you!
Store74 takes inspiration from the visual art movement genius of Andy Warhol crossed with the ever increasing (and very popular) bicycle hobby.
This is a highly colourful and very “Pop Art” T-shirt guaranteed to catch the eye on even the longest cycle rides!
Go on, express yourself with art!

Tee Colour: Grey

name: 100% Rock
description:
Tired of being asked what you think about 1 Directions new song? Exhausted by the endless singing competitions on your television? Then it’s about time you threw that TV set out of the nearest window!
Unleash the inner Rock star and grab life by both hands!
Plug in your electric guitar and crank the volume up high as Store74 helps you in your quest for 100% Rock acknowledgement!
Be loud, be proud and make your own Rock god history…

Tee Colour: Black (of course!)

name: Wookie Want Cookie Tee
description:
Wookie translated means “people of the trees”.
They are tall, hairy humanoids that inhabit the planet Kashyyyk.
Despite their fearsome appearance these mammals are usually gentle, although they are prone to devastating fits of rage when provoked!
These rage explosions are caused mainly by a lack of sugary treats.
Legend says that they were enticed out of their forest homes to join the Galactic civil war with a packet of chocolate cookies.
Always keep a biscuit in your pocket as all Wookies want cookies!

Tee Colour: Light Blue

name: Hazard County Tee
description:
With their 1969 Dodge charger stock car christened the “General Lee” the Duke boys have been creating mischief and mayhem throughout Hazard County for years.
Join Jefferson Davis “Boss” Hogg and county sheriff Roscoe P. Coltrane in their mission to catch the illegal moonshine brewers.
Unarmed but extremely dangerous, the Duke boys must not be approached as they are a menace to society…

Tee Colour: Sage Green

name: Day Release Patient Tee
description:
Do you find your partner/brother/friend slightly confusing?
Is their cranium misfiring? Leading to bouts of insanity?
Then this Tee is for them!
Store74 sends out a warning to others that they are on a day release program from the local ward!
Encourage them to participate in one final act of bonkersness before they are returned to their padded cell.
Pat yourself on the back for helping out these lovable fruit-loops.

Tee Colour: Blue

name: Gift Voucher
description:
Confuzzled about what to get? Then get a gift voucher and leave the decision making to them! We have vouchers in multiples of £10 - just add one to your shopping cart or more for an extra special treat! We will email your gift voucher within 24 hours for the whole value purchased, then you can print it out or forward the email to the lucky recipient! Yay! 

PS: If you want to buy vouchers for more than one person then add a message to PayPal when you check-out and we can email separate vouchers! Yeah baby!

name: -0.07 Licence to Chill Tee
description:
From Store74 with love!
I’ve been expecting you Mr Bond…
With the temperature dropping and the nights closing in there might just be a “skyfall” of snow!
Her majesty’s secret service have changed Bonds licence to chill number to -0.07 making him a secret agent of the cold war.
A great tee for all Bond fans to enjoy!
Go on, treat yourself “you only live twice” (sorry)
 
Tee Colour: Light Blue

name: Up & Atom Tee
description:
It has been said that during the 20th century, man harnessed the power of the atom. We made atomic bombs and generated electricity by nuclear power. We even split the atom into smaller pieces called subatomic particles.
Right, science lesson over!
Do you need an atomic kick-start in the morning? A Nerdy nudge? Then this tee is for you!
Located inside the atomic structure lies 2 words “Up” & “And” giving you an energising boost of “up and atom!”
Become that positively charged nucleus! (But do not surround yourself with negatively charged electrons).
 
Tee Colour: Yellow

name: Transformers (Robots Eating Pies) Tee
description:
Let’s roll out!
In celebration of that great animated robotic series in the 1980’s comes this superb tee…
With hit movies now on the autobots list they are becoming increasingly old and lazy!
No longer are they described as “robots in disguise” but “robots eating pies”
Hollywood has changed them, and earth is set for a whole load of Megatron trouble!
Store74 guaran(tee) the theme tune will be whistled whilst you wear!

Tee Colour: Light Blue

name: MAMIL (Middle Aged Men In Lycra) Tee
description:
Not to be confused with four-legged vertebrates with a four chambered heart!
This is an all-round action hero cyclist who doesn’t care that he is a “Middle-Aged Man In Lycra”
He proudly dons his (very tight) superhero shorts/ leggings and pounds the streets (or tracks...) on his chosen pedal powered vehicle!
Recognise these individuals in all of their glory before they become extinct.
Is it a bird? Is it a plane? No it’s a MAMIL…

Tee Colour: Red

name: D.N.D.G. (Dweeb, Nerd, Dork, Geek) Venn Tee
description:
Dweeb, Nerd, Dork, Geek?
A great informative Venn diagram tee that works out who and where you are in life!
Three overlapping circles examine the relationships between being Intelligent, socially inept and obsessive.
Reading between the lines will then lead you to your distinct personality!
Recently tested on Store74 colleagues and 100% accurate! (I’m a Dork by the way - our web tech is such a Geek!).
Be proud, be yourself!

Tee Colour: Sage Green

name: Hi-5 (To the face!) Tee
description:
We all know one…
That certain person who in every situation from sports to work has to high five you after a good result!
You can tolerate (maybe) the odd high five but it’s time to let them know that enough is enough.
Let Store 74 explain that the next one will be (literally) in their face!
Please feel free to send us any before and after pictures to add to our “pink cheeks” office gallery…

Tee Colour: Sage Green

name: Earn Your Stripes Tee
description:
Are you a sociable animal?
A unique individual that stands out from the crowd?
Then this great tee is for you!
Let work colleagues, bosses know that you are willing to work extra hard to “earn your stripes”.
You may not be fully domesticated and resemble an ass, but you will get to where you want to be in life (whatever it throws at you).
A positive message to the herd!


Tee Colour: White

name: Sarcasm Loading Tee
description:
Are you king (or queen!) of the quip? General of the bitter gibe?
Then let StoreSeventyFour help you along your way...
A large loading box adds as a warning to others that your sarcastic nature is starting to download!
Feel free to explode your vocal inflections on the masses before it reaches 100%!
Unleash the wit and cultivate the caustic!


Tee Colour: Natural

name: Please Speak Quietly (Hangover) Tee
description:
Heavy night out? Head banging like a pneumatic drill?
Energy levels resembling a grandmother watching the Antiques Roadshow?
If all boxes are ticked then this cheeky tee is for you.
Let everyone know that after partying like a weekend warrior you need some quiet time to recover.
Bold and in-your-face fonts clearly explain (even to idiots) that wrapping you up in cotton wool is on today's list.


Tee Colour: Natural

name: Woman Hunter Tee
description:
The weekend is almost approaching and the sound of wild women stampeding towards the nearest social venue fills the air. You are the only one who can save us!
The Woman Hunter tee comes with a snipers crosshairs to lock onto female targets.
Aim your sights, pull the trigger and bag yourself a wild catch!
Warning: The Woman hunter tee must be fully utilised in brightly lit places. It cannot be blamed for poor personal judgement!


Tee Colour: Light Grey

name: OMO (Opinions May Offend!) Tee
description:
Do you suffer from foot in mouth disease?
Are you as subtle as a brick in tricky situations?
Then this t shirt is definitely for you!
A large, bold distressed caution sign explains that your opinions may offend...
Be relaxed and confident in the knowledge that your unhinged big mouth will now be accepted into social situations! 
Disclaimer: Store 74 cannot be held responsible for any arguments or fights caused by this tee.


Tee Colour: Natural

name: Having a Giraffe Tee
description:
Famous for their long, blue tongues and even-toes this fantastic dominant mammal bears the responsibility of explaining how you feel!
With increasing work hours, lower pay and nightmare bosses (yes, we've been there!) our beloved giraffe gently explains how not to stretch your talents to breaking point.
Subtle but effective without being rude!


Tee Colour: White

name: Not a Drill Tee
description:
He's small, feisty and full of nuts!
Robot ST74 is a highly functional electro-mechanical machine that loves to keep busy.
Sadly, he was developed without a new super brain so becomes fixated with minor objects!
He's a symbol that reminds us that sometimes it's not great to state the obvious...

Tee Colour: White

name: Game Over Tee ~ WHITE
description:
Retro, arcaded and a brilliant culture icon!
In celebration of the first video game designed in 1978 our two pixelated enemy aliens have destroyed your final laser cannon to earn a well deserved "Game Over".
The alien invasion is successful this time and the war is now over.

Tee Colour: White

name: Game Over Tee ~ GREEN
description:
Retro, arcaded and a brilliant culture icon!
In celebration of the first video game designed in 1978 our two pixelated enemy aliens have destroyed your final laser cannon to earn a well deserved "Game Over".
The alien invasion is successful this time and the war is now over.

Tee Colour: Green

name: Vintage Camper Van Tee
description:
This vintage old skool camper van brings back memories of holidays, surfing and freedom!
Quietly parked and waiting for dawn to break this iconic motor vehicle reminds us to explore our surroundings and to break the chains of modern life.
Bring back the fun of the old days!


Tee Colour: Light Grey

name: Destruction Robot Tee
description:
ST74 gets an upgrade!
With a new super brain installed our (once friendly) robot has turned into a menacing machine!
After busily rampaging and damaging a nearby apartment block he (rather cheekily) stops for a sit down and rest.
This great hand drawn design reminds us that flying into a destructive rage is not the best answer!

Tee Colour: White

name: Stoopid Cow Tee
description:
Moove on baby!
Use our Devine bovine to get that last (bad) relationship out of your system.
Just let the world know that she wasn't "the one" and your true feelings towards her.
It's not subtle, but explains that you're not ready for the manure heap just yet!
(Future shirts will be balanced out with a female version...honest)


Tee Colour: White

name: Grizzly Bear Tee
description:
Do you ever wake up after a hibernation period hungry, agitated and hairy?
If yes, this tee is exactly what you need.
Let fellow friends, colleagues or annoying people know that after your state of inactivity, you have woken up to a "Grizzly" mood.
Watch as people give you a wide berth and hide in fear as you approach them. Just stay away from campsites and hunters bearing (pun intended) large guns!


Tee Colour: Natural

name: Binary Geek Tee
description:
Arise, King of the Geeks this one's for you...
This eye-catching design uses each letters special binary code to great effect!
Distinctive & subtle - use as an ideal talking point.
(Just don't bore us all explaining the other 22 letters unique binary codes!).

Tee Colour: Grey
